add java connector(file:-mysql-connector-java-5.1.47.jar) in following path in lib directory
Project_name
------------WebContent
-----------------------WEB-INF
------------------------------lib

create two datbase tables
1) users
2) student

user 
+----------+-------------+------+-----+---------+----------------+
| Field    | Type        | Null | Key | Default | Extra          |
+----------+-------------+------+-----+---------+----------------+
| id       | int(11)     | NO   | PRI | NULL    | auto_increment |
| username | varchar(50) | NO   |     | NULL    |                |
| password | varchar(10) | NO   |     | NULL    |                |
| block    | int(1)      | NO   |     | NULL    |                |
+----------+-------------+------+-----+---------+----------------+

student
+---------+-------------+------+-----+---------+----------------+
| Field   | Type        | Null | Key | Default | Extra          |
+---------+-------------+------+-----+---------+----------------+
| id      | int(11)     | NO   | PRI | NULL    | auto_increment |
| stuname | varchar(10) | NO   |     | NULL    |                |
| sturoll | int(5)      | NO   | UNI | NULL    |                |
| stumark | int(3)      | NO   |     | NULL    |                |
+---------+-------------+------+-----+---------+----------------+
